.RS
.IP \(bu 4
macOS 12.0 (Monterey) or later
.IP \(bu 4
Intel x86_64 or Apple Silicon arm64 architecture
.IP \(bu 4
2GB+ RAM recommended
.IP \(bu 4
100MB+ free storage for temporary files
